import sys

def main():
    s = sys.stdin.readline().strip()
    t = ''
    u = ''
    for i in range(len(s)):
        t += s[i]
        u = min(u, t[::-1] + s[i + 1:])
    print(u)

if __name__ == '__main__':
    main()
